review:
Weeeeell, it's a great game with three but(t)s:
- I just don't have the reaction speed for level 3 stuff even if I'm a little tired;
- There doesn't seem to be a single tutorial for all of the mechanics, so it's not super easy to get into after a big break;
- You only have 2 health. That feels like very little in some longer sequences between checkpoints. But it's just probably my ineptitude talking.
